      "relevance": "The paper discusses five mass extinction events as the foundation for considering whether a sixth extinction is underway."
    },
    {
      "name": "Biodiversity",
      "relation": "uses",
      "entity_type": "concept",
      "wikipedia_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Biodiversity",
